### 用户注册 第一步
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register?email=1876056356@qq.com&password=Test123!

### 用户登录 第四步
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login?email=1876056356@qq.com&password=NewPass123!

### 完整密码重置流程
1. 发送验证码 → 2. 验证验证码 → 3. 重置密码

### 发送验证码 第二步
POST http://localhost:8080/api/verification/send-code
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "1876056356@qq.com"
}

### 验证验证码 可选的
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/verification/verify
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "1876056356@qq.com",
  "code": "675757"
}

### 重置密码 第三步
POST http://localhost:8080/api/verification/reset-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "1876056356@qq.com",
  "code": "431753",
  "newPassword": "NewPass123!"
}